title: Karlos Dansby comes up with big plays for Cleveland Browns, just like he said he would
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Sports - Yesterday 
Browns linebacker Karlos Dansby picked off Peyton Manning twice, and ran one of those back for a touchdown to give the Browns a lead.
